<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Upa Chunga</author>
<hymn_number>108</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kalvaria Na hehpihna tui bang a hung liena,
 Kei gilo thalek gamgaw mun haksa ah;
 Dam dii diei in a hung luonga,
 A chunga ginna lawng bawl dan ka thiem thei puoi.

[V2]
 Panpih ding Thagau ka ngai,
 Panpih ding Thagau ka ngai ie;
 Noah kuong bawl pihpa Thagau ka ngai.

[V3]
 2. Lalpa, Zion zawtna lampi Thagau panpih loh chun,
 Amau chitna mangin kuo a hung thei die?
 Lalpa kei chu ka hung thei puoi,
 Na chitna leh ka thiemna a kikalh ziekin.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa, Na khut lopi ngakin gitloh tuipi chungah,
 A dawn umlo nausen bangin ka uma;
 Na hehpihna a hung tunga,
 Ka ginna tawh kiphun kipak in ka um sek.

[V5]
 4. Ka hukdampa, ka Lal Krista tui bang A hung let tieng,
 Ka gimna leh ka buoina chup mang intin;
 A hehpihnan ei huk intin,
 Amah kawma chawl dingin ei pui lut tana.</lyrics>
<title>Panpihtu Thagau</title>
</song>